Anglo American Platinum First-Half Headline Earnings Per Share Increased

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-07-11T06:03:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/anglo-american-platinum-first-half-headline-earnings-per-share-increased.html
Anglo American Platinum Ltd. said
first-half headline earnings per share increased to between
11.31 rand and 13.36 rand from the 10.28 rand reported a year
earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  